1. You needn't buy so much strawberry. Our mother bought two kilos yesterday.
2. I must hurry. I may be late for my train. 3. She decided that she should not go to
London this year. 4. Need she take so many things? It isn't cold in England in winter.
5. May he take your cassette? - No, he may not. 6. The rain may stop soon. 7. I may
not spend so much money. 8. Can you hear that noise? 9. Can you see this girl?
10. I cannot eat so much. 11. He was allowed to pass the exams much earlier.
12. You may use this tape recorder. 13. She wasn't able to help him. 14. She might
ring. 15. She may change her mind. So you should agree.
